FBIS4-9191 "dreeu078_i_94008" FBIS-EEU-94-078 Daily Report 21 Apr 1994 BOSNIA-HERZEGOVINA Serbs Give Withdrawal Ultimatum to Army in Gorazde Serbs Give Withdrawal Ultimatum to Army in Gorazde LD2104171494 Zagreb Radio Croatia Network in Serbo-Croatian 1700 GMT 21 Apr 94 LD2104171494 Zagreb Radio Croatia Network Serbo-Croatian BFN [Text] The Serbian aggressor forces have issued an ultimatum to the forces of the Bosnia-Herzegovina Army in Gorazde, demanding that they withdraw completely from the right bank of the River Drina. They can remain on the left bank only in the 3-km circle around the town center. This has been announced from the Embassy of the Republic of Bosnia-Herzegovina in Zagreb.
